sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 用户
    participant FE as LifePilot
    participant BE as LifePilotServer
    participant RT as 工作流路由
    participant MCP as LifePilot_mcp
    participant RAG as ai-server
    participant DB as 多源存储

    User->>FE: 输入请求
    FE->>BE: 提交请求
    BE->>RT: 意图识别
    RT->>MCP: 任务域操作
    RT->>RAG: 知识域操作
    MCP->>DB: 写入或查询任务数据
    RAG->>DB: 查询知识索引与文档数据
    DB-->>BE: 返回结果
    BE-->>FE: 流式返回
    FE-->>User: 展示反馈